=> Understand HTTP (Foundation of APIs)

Client → HTTP Request → Server
Server → HTTP Response → Client

Example:

Client sends request:

GET /hello

Server returns response:

200 OK
Hello World

=> Key components of HTTP request:

Method
URL
Headers
Body

Example request:

POST /login
Content-Type: application/json

Body:

{
 "username":"ashish",
 "password":"123"
}

Server responds:

{
 "token":"abc123"
}


